{"tid":1357111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警在  橋上  向示威者開槍","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:35:38.000Z","uid":257736,"like":71,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"3c397c4e95d72c703698efb0e7fca9d783562b44","tid":1357111,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:01:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Now 拍 到野</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">黑警 竟然在橋上面開槍</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>死黑警癲左，以為自己響戰場呀？</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">拍攝到當晚在中區警署外行人天橋有速龍小隊監察橋下情況，<strong>期間警員驅趕記者，在無任何警告下，向橋下的示威者發射橡膠子彈</strong>，橋上留下彈殼。幾分鐘後，再有警員在未有示警下發射胡椒球彈。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>真係好嬲好想喊，做警察，竟然企響 當權者果邊，欺壓平民百姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=356494&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356494%26refer%3D&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=41fcd6a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356494%26refer%3D&h=a3ab07eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=356494&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"ac046e887bc7adffe117102e2d57c59b1c87830b","tid":1357111,"uid":194298,"like":13,"dislike":